 </stability>
 <license uri="http://www.php.net/license">PHP License 3.01</license>
 <notes>
Full modernization for the PHP 8.x era.

- PHP 8.0 - 8.5 floor; libstatgrab 0.92+ floor.
- New Statgrab class with method-style accessors and class constants.
- Richer return shapes: host/cpu/fs/iface/process structs gained the
  fields libstatgrab added since the 2006 era.
- BC fixes: page_stats/page_stats_diff de-swapped, process gid/egid
  return the actual gid/egid (not uid/euid).
- BC break: sg_user_stats() returns per-user records instead of a flat
  username array; libstatgrab dropped the underlying name_list field.
- Numeric counters now return int instead of stringified numbers.

See CHANGELOG.md for the full list.
 </notes>
